oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sister Cities of Nashville
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Nashville (Tenn.);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (blue, yellow and green on white) announcing Sister Cities of Nashville, celebrating 25 years of Friendships around the World 1990-2015. Sister cities include Taiyuan, China; Tamworth, Australia; Belfast Northern Ireland; Caen, France; Edmonton, Canada; Kamakura, Japan; Mendoza Argentina; and Magdeburg, Germany.
